data.value: 1. First go to File -> Open Folder -> 'Your albums folder' 2. Go to FIle -> Keep Folder -> 'Where do you want to save albums when you press Keep Album' 3. You can navigate through paths in 'Directories List Box' 4. Once you have selected the album, press Play/Stop and you can go to the next/previous song with the buttons above the songs List Box
